room_title: Escape room "The Heist" by Amazing Escape Room in Bridgewater
room_address: 326 Route 22 West Suites 13/14B Green Brook, New Jersey, NJ 08812
room_description: You have joined a notorious crime syndicate and your mob boss has a job for you to prove your worth, rob The Staten Island Bank. You only have 60 minutes to acquire as much cash as you can from the bank vault before the cops arrive! Can you escape? More importantly, how much loot can you get first?
